high_descs: Turn and go left and then turn to the right to face the trash can.
Pick the apple up out of the trash can.
Go right and then right again to face the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door again and take the apple out.
Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the trash can.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left, move to face the trash past the counter on your right.
Pick up the apple in the trash can.
Bring the apple to the other side of the room, to the fridge on your right.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Bring the chilled apple back to the trash can on your right.
Put the chilled apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn and go to the trash can that is to the left of the counter.
Pick up the apple that is in the trash can.
With the apple in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge. Place the apple on the top right shelf and close the door. Open the door and grab the apple on the top right shelf.
With the apple in hand go to the trash can.
Place the apple in front of the silver object that is in the trash can.
